Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.31,0:02:35.42,KYO OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\3c4720E8\t(730,980,\3cDF994B)}七転八倒で到着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.42,0:02:38.36,KYO OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\3cDF994B}既存理論でカクメイ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.36,0:02:42.18,KYO OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\3cDF994B\t(1200,1400,\3c4720E8)}誰もが予測不能の連鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.18,0:02:45.03,KYO OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\3c993A1E}虚ろう瞳に映る
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.03,0:02:48.11,KYO OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\3c993A1E\t(1800,2100,\3c25CAE3)}有象無象は御免
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.11,0:02:51.98,KYO OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\3c25CAE3\t(450,520,\3c2C1C95)}この世の理、手繰って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.98,0:02:54.44,KYO OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}心中 警戒 絶後 消失 如来像
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.44,0:02:56.78,KYO OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}虚構 徹頭 徹尾 真実 風来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:03:01.44,KYO OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\3c4F1D73}モノノケトケモノ ヒトも、割と同じ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.44,0:03:06.05,KYO OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\3c4F1D73}今、走る言葉がつまづいても
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.05,0:03:11.45,KYO OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\3cAC2846}くだらない話でもちゃんと聞いてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.45,0:03:16.50,KYO OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}例え細くてもほどけないように
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:20.12,KYO OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\3c691F3D}不確かな未来でも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.12,0:03:22.50,KYO OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\3c691F3D\t(1150,1250,\3c2C1C95)}掴んで撃ち砕け
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.31,0:02:35.42,KYO OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\3c4720E8\t(730,980,\3cDF994B)}跌跌撞撞地抵達這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.42,0:02:38.36,KYO OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\3cDF994B}以現存理論發動革命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.36,0:02:42.18,KYO OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\3cDF994B\t(1200,1400,\3c4720E8)}無可預知的蝴蝶效應
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.18,0:02:45.03,KYO OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\3c993A1E}無視那空洞的瞳中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.03,0:02:48.11,KYO OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\3c993A1E\t(1800,2100,\3c25CAE3)}映出的虛妄之形骸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.11,0:02:51.98,KYO OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\3c25CAE3\t(450,520,\3c2C1C95)}只將此世真理攫取於手中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.98,0:02:54.44,KYO OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}心中 警戒 絕後 消失 如來像
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.44,0:02:56.78,KYO OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}虛構 徹頭 徹尾 真實 風來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:03:01.44,KYO OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\3c4F1D73}無論鬼怪或妖魔 都與人類無甚區別
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.44,0:03:06.05,KYO OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\3c4F1D73}即使這激揚的話語始終難以傳達
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.05,0:03:11.45,KYO OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\3cAC2846}也請你仔細聽聽這些徒然的遐想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.45,0:03:16.50,KYO OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}哪怕是只存在細微可能性的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:20.12,KYO OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\3c691F3D}也定會被我們掌握手中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.12,0:03:22.50,KYO OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\3c691F3D\t(1150,1250,\3c2C1C95)}打破世間的虛實
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.88,0:22:43.57,KYO EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur2}どこへ行こうか　夢から覚めたら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.16,0:22:51.90,KYO EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur2}サファイアの夜　なまぬるい風　潜めて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.15,0:23:01.14,KYO EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur2}真っ暗なほどに　きれいな瞳が瞬く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.25,0:23:09.12,KYO EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur2}そっと抱き寄せて　優しい獣の声で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.13,0:23:11.16,KYO EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur2}You can do, we can do, try
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.76,0:23:16.35,KYO EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur2}お遊びのまま　いじらしいまま
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.52,0:23:19.99,KYO EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur2}君らしく暴れて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.97,0:23:24.26,KYO EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur2}ふざけないなんて　つまらない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.36,0:23:28.93,KYO EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur2}僕ららしく踊らせて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.53,0:23:34.65,KYO EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur2}I'll save the last dance for you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.88,0:22:43.57,KYO EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur2}從夢境醒來後  我們將要前往何方？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.16,0:22:51.90,KYO EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur2}迎著溫蘊的風  銷聲匿跡在藍寶石般的午夜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.15,0:23:01.14,KYO EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur2}如深淵般動人的雙瞳  迸射著光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.25,0:23:09.12,KYO EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur2}讓我將你悄然攬至身畔  如野獸般柔情低語
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.13,0:23:11.16,KYO EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur2}You  can  do,  we  can  do,  try
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.76,0:23:16.35,KYO EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur2}就這樣玩世不恭  這樣楚楚可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.52,0:23:19.99,KYO EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur2}釋放僅屬於你的狂野吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.97,0:23:24.26,KYO EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur2}若不縱情喧囂  又有何樂趣可言？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.36,0:23:28.93,KYO EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur2}舞出屬於你我的風采吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.53,0:23:34.65,KYO EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur2}I'll save the last dance for you
